data.description: Lots of space in this renovated 4BR/3BA home. Beautiful upgrades. Great variety in bedroom usage with two primaries, plus another bedroom has a bonus area and its own private entrance which can be an in-law space. This one is a must see! Established Glenview Historic District. No subject to or assignments.
